This book is a guide to using Lists on the Texas Instruments Graphing Calculators. It emphasizes the details as implemented on the TI-83 and TI-84 families of calculators. The differences in in details for the TI-86 and TI-89 calculators are available by following the links found at appropriate places. [[TI-Lists/TI-86|(TI-86)]]
